<HEADLINE> Sandra Bernhard Performs in Israel </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TEL AVIV, Israel (AP) -- Sandra Bernhard pulled no punches about  
the Israeli-Arab conflict during a weekend performance. 
</P>
<P>
	Israelis and Palestinians? Both are ``lazy'' people who deserve  
one another, the comedian said. She was taking a break making jabs 
at celebrity culture during her ``I'm Still Here ... Damn It'' show 
